	* configure.ac, po/ja.po, THANKS, NEWS: Add ja translations, thanks to
	  Daichi Kawahata <daichik@users.sourceforge.net>.
	* docs/reference/tmpl/*.sgml: Regenerate with updated gtk-doc.

